{"title":"SimWorks by Velocity Polished Standalone Rims","link":"https://theradavist.com/simworks-by-velocity-polished-standalone-rims/","date":1709841644000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/IMG_2741-1.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/IMG_2741-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/IMG_2741-1.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/IMG_2741-1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/IMG_2741-1.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>SimWorks knows the demand for polished rims is high, so they teamed up with Velocity USA to offer its <a href=\"https://www.sim.works/products/standalone-001-polished\" target=\"_blank\">Standalone rims in a mirror finish</a>…<span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/IMG_9180.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/IMG_9180.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/IMG_9180.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/IMG_9180.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/IMG_9180.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>SimWorks’ newest offering from Velocity is a high-polished update to our Standalone 001 rim profile. Otherwise identical to the existing <a href=\"https://www.sim.works/products/standalone-001-polished\" target=\"_blank\">Standalone 001</a> model, this updated finish is a response to fielded requests for this option.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-People-and-Product-156.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-People-and-Product-156.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-People-and-Product-156.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-People-and-Product-156.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-People-and-Product-156.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-People-and-Product-156.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-People-and-Product-156.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-People-and-Product-156.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>The brand brought its updated Doppo ‘Ronin’ to the MADE Bike Show in Portland in August, set up with a set of these beautiful Polished Standalone rims and received a steady stream of inquiries and compliments.</p>\n<p>As a thank you for the warm welcome, the Standalone 001 rim will now be offered in a polished finish with both machined and non-machined sidewall variants and in all three sizes—26”, 27.5”, and 29”. All rims are still 32-hole drilling only.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SIMWORKS-Velocity-StandalonePolish1.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SIMWORKS-Velocity-StandalonePolish1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SIMWORKS-Velocity-StandalonePolish1.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SIMWORKS-Velocity-StandalonePolish1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SIMWORKS-Velocity-StandalonePolish1.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>SimWorks – Standalone 001 Rim Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Sizes: 700c/29″ (622 BSD)</li>\n<li>650b/27.5″ (584 BSD)</li>\n<li>26″ (559 BSD)</li>\n<li>Material: Aluminum</li>\n<li>Drilling: 32 hole</li>\n<li>Tire Compatibility: Clincher/Tubeless</li>\n<li>Width: 30mm outer / 25mm-hook to hook internal</li>\n<li>Height: 21.6mm</li>\n<li>Optimal Tire Width: 45mm-65mm</li>\n<li>Weight: 580g (559) / 605g (584) / 640g (622)</li>\n<li>ERD: 26″: (537mm) / 650b/27.5″: (564mm) 29″: (602mm)</li>\n<li>Price: $179 MSW / $169 NMSW</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.sim.works/products/standalone-001-polished\" target=\"_blank\">SimWorks</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/simworks-by-velocity-polished-standalone-rims/\">SimWorks by Velocity Polished Standalone Rims</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"affbf976bb3587e66206f7804fb26a7ba88063986155808941cd14a2db556278","category":"Cycling"}